  "description": "A two-chamber refrigerator with a bottom freezer is a 2022 model of the Gorenje brand, which can be attributed to solutions in the middle price segment. With a body size of 179x60x59 cm, the unit has a total volume of 292 liters, which should definitely be enough for families of two or three people. The Full No Frost system also belongs to the chips of the device: it provides dynamic cooling and eliminates the formation of frost on the walls, so manual defrosting is not required in the refrigerator or freezer compartment. Refrigerator Gorenje NRK 6181 PW4 provides an 85-liter freezer with three retractable transparent boxes. The freezing capacity is quite modest, so that no more than 4 kg of newly added products can be frozen here per day. Autonomous preservation of cold is declared at around 10 hours. The 207-liter refrigerator has four open shelves and one container for vegetables and fruits. Among other features, it is worth highlighting a low noise level (up to 39 dB - class C), energy consumption F (according to the old marking, it corresponds to an A + rating), the presence of traditional controls in the form of rotary switches.",
